invalid type: string "# GST Validation Rule \n \n## When this rule applies \nDuring tax validation stage. \n \n## Rule \n- GST amount must match applicable GST rate \n- GSTIN must be present for taxable invoices \n \n## Violation Conditions \n- Missing GSTIN Ôćĺ non-compliant \n- GST mismatch Ôćĺ incorrect taxation \n \n## Severity \n- Missing GSTIN Ôćĺ HIGH \n- Mismatch Ôćĺ MEDIUM \n \n          